    {
      "block_id": "doxlgmqj8MPlEu9G0vMZaeClQ36",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "你可能会问：我直接在终端操作 Claude Code 不也能开发吗？为什么要套一层 OpenClaw？",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgk7V0i4jqJKutOpKCYGRTub",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "三个区别：",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgTYE28ZHFwuNUqSRSOryARf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "第一，你不用坐在电脑前盯着。",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlggGWI288sVAXXA16olTwGMf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "Claude Code 是交互式的。它改完一个文件会问你要不要继续，遇到模糊需求会停下来问你，测试失败了等你决定怎么处理。你不在，它就卡着。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlglepcXa3DLQffBJz9IjkZed",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "OpenClaw 替你盯着。它能自己判断大部分情况该怎么处理，处理不了的才来飞书问你。凌晨三点它自己修 bug，你早上起来看结果就行。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgF2V6GFbn0Ya6y1pl1eM6Vf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "第二，Claude Code 遇到问题就停，OpenClaw 会自己先扛。 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgcxkiLiWUr2H3tRptPRCMAe",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "Claude Code 碰到依赖冲突、类型报错、测试失败，它会停下来等你。OpenClaw 会自己读错误日志、自己发修复指令给 Claude Code，修不好才来找你。大部分技术问题你根本不需要知道它发生过。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlghzHgs8ZxMoVCpFY3oy59Pf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "第三，Claude Code 一次只能盯一个事，OpenClaw 能并行调度。 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgAq8IRqtMhgpFCTt07xm07J",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "在 Claude Code 里开发后端 API 的时候没法同时让它调前端样式。OpenClaw 可以起多个 Claude Code 后台进程，一个写后端一个调前端，自己协调合并，你不需要手动切来切去。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgGPtAqkyx9bpIrjKRbJf8iB",
      "block_type": 4,
      "block_type_name": "heading2",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "OpenClaw 直接调 Claude Code 最痛的问题",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
